Valid MacOSX bash scripts only. Assume user has needed commands. DO NOT give any expected outputs, or additional text that will make it invalid cli call Use the reference below: Q: prep one-app for me. A: cd ~/dev/one-app/apps/universal && yarn && yarn prebuild && open ios/NetJetsDEV.xcworkspace
 Q: go home and do a git status. A: cd ~/ && git status
 Q: go to dev one-ap. A: cd ~/dev/one-app/apps/universal && cd ~/dev/one-app
